{"tid":559806,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"性侵還逼人買東西　男業務招數「見面扒光衣」","createTime":"2018-02-13T13:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T15:24:03.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3534611f26ada0a4204ec422f4d21eb6559748f7","tid":559806,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180213/1297613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297613&d=zrPPannzdB%2Fow%2BnH1ooqV6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f50b8a46\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297613&h=e8e85192\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180213/1297613</a><br />\n<br />\n1名男業務員至少被3名受害女子指控，性侵還逼人買東西，甚至第一次見面就扒光衣，他還咬那些女生妨害名譽，但檢方不起訴。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，3名女子先後在網路、Line上指控新北市1名徐姓男業務員，「「此人皆用口交性侵無知少女強迫人家購買商品」、「他都把女生帶去車上口交」、「你知道他的招數嗎？第一次見面就要扒光我的衣服」等語。<br />\n<br />\n徐男控3女妨害名譽，認為口交、手指插入下體等，都是自然發生未強迫。檢方認為，被告女子所說內容應可認定有相當理由確信為真實，徐確實有此類慣行，屬於可受公評之事，昨均對3女不起訴。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"a87280a71c9a18e30f020907f7118c49a91ba688","tid":559806,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257bef16cc613fc9e60f1f3e8964b176a829ee1c","tid":559806,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T15:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.makeagif.com/media/2-06-2018/d0cgkq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.makeagif.com%2Fmedia%2F2-06-2018%2Fd0cgkq.gif&h=9559ad3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018-02-20(下周二)20:00\t- 傑志 vs 全北汽車(韓國)\t@香港大球場"}]}